refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.parameters;
result
Le paramètre result provient d'un appel à la fonction cubrid_execute, la fonction cubrid_query ou la fonction cubrid_prepare.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Exemple avec cubrid_num_rows


<?php
$conn = cubrid_connect("localhost", 33000, "demodb", "dba");

$req = cubrid_execute($conn, "SELECT * FROM code");

$row_num = cubrid_num_rows($req);
$col_num = cubrid_num_cols($req);

printf("Row Num: %d\nColumn Num: %d\n", $row_num, $col_num);

cubrid_disconnect($conn);
?>


   &example.outputs;


Row Num: 6
Column Num: 2
